data.title: Mpaa Film Numbers 52000
data.meta_description: Mpaa Film Numbers 52000 - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document lists the MPAA certificate numbers issued to films from 1934 to 1935. It provides the certificate number, year, film title linked to IMDB, and occasionally additional details for each certified film from #0 to around #550 for this time period. The MPAA certificate numbers were displayed in film credits to indicate approval under the production code.
